	To create a custom Collections page 
	  1) create a new "Collections" Page (set page Template to page.collections) 
	  2) Add your new page to the main navigation (Name your menu item "Collections", page type "Collections")
	  3) Go to 'Customize Theme'
	  	3a) click on 'collections' in main nav on the preview page
	  	3b) Here you can edit your banner and how many collections per row (three is suggested)
	  	3c) Save and view your changes, view your content
